put.description:
Updates the Comment.
 
Sample request:
 
    PUT projects/{projectId}/topics/{topicId}/comments/{commentId} 
    { 
        "comment": "Comment value", 
        "viewpoint_guid": "c5a73cc9-b155-4556-8963-bc7dc13c6fd2", 
        "reply_to_comment_guid": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6" 
    }

Updates the document reference.
 
Note: 'url' and 'document_guid' are mutually exclusive.
 
Note: 'guid' is a required field and will replace the existing 'guid'.
 
Sample request:
 
    PUT Projects/{projectId}/Topics/{topicId}/document_references/{documentReferenceId} 
    { 
        "guid": "0e367f48-3ff0-4523-81cc-2b7259d74f36", 
        "document_guid": "472ab37a-6122-448e-86fc-86503183b520", 
        "description": "The building owners global design parameters for buildings. - updated2" 
    }

Updates the referenced files of the topic.
 
Sample request:
 
    PUT Projects/{projectId}/Topics/{topicId}/files 
     [{ 
        "ifc_project": "0J$yPqHBD12v72y4qF6XcD", 
        "file_name": "OfficeBuilding_Architecture_0001.ifc", 
        "reference": "https://example.com/files/0J$yPqHBD12v72y4qF6XcD_0001.ifc" 
    }, { 
        "ifc_project": "3hwBHP91jBRwPsmyf$3Hea", 
        "file_name": "OfficeBuilding_Heating_0003.ifc", 
        "reference": "https://example.com/files/3hwBHP91jBRwPsmyf$3Hea_0003.ifc" 
    }]

Updates the related topics.
 
Sample request:
 
    PUT Projects/{projectId}/Topics/{topicId}/related_topics 
     [{ 
         "related_topic_guid": "db49df2b-0e42-473b-a3ee-f7b785d783c4" 
     }, { 
         "related_topic_guid": "6963a846-54d1-4050-954d-607cd5e48aa3" 
     }]

patch.description:
Updates Comments in batch for the specified Trimble Connect Project.
 
Sample request:
 
    PATCH /projects/{projectId}/comments/batch 
    { 
      "items" : [ 
        { 
          "comment": "Updated Comment value 1", 
          "topic_guid": "01070301-3A04-B43B-A713-5E676BEF8338", 
          "guid": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6", 
          "viewpoint_guid": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6", 
          "reply_to_comment_guid": "c5a73cc9-b155-4556-8963-bc7dc13c6fd2" 
        }, 
        { 
